<rss version="2.0" xmlns:content="http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" xmlns:ss="http://contenthub.aol.com/slideshow/"><channel><title><![CDATA[Engadget is a web magazine with obsessive daily coverage of everything new in gadgets and consumer electronics]]></title><link/> https://www.engadget.com/ <description><![CDATA[Engadget is a web magazine with obsessive daily coverage of everything new in gadgets and consumer electronics]]></description><language> en-US</language><copyright>版权所有雅虎 2023</copyright><pubDate> Sat, 11 Nov 2023 22:42:35 +0000</pubDate><generator>雅虎 http://yahoo.com </generator><item><title><![CDATA[SpaceX workers face above-average injury rates as Musk prioritizes Mars over safety, report finds]]></title><description type="html"><![CDATA[<p> <a data-i13n="elm:context_link;elmt:doNotAffiliate;cpos:1;pos:1" class="no-affiliate-link" href="https://www.reuters.com/investigates/special-report/spacex-musk-safety/" data-original-link="https://www.reuters.com/investigates/special-report/spacex-musk-safety/"><em>路透社</em></a>对 SpaceX 不安全工作条件的调查发现，自 2014 年以来，已有 600 多人受伤，但迄今为止尚未公开报道。报告中引用的现任和前任员工指责首席执行官埃隆·马斯克(Elon Musk)过于紧迫的最后期限和对官僚主义的憎恨，称他“尽快”将人类送上火星的目标导致公司走捷径并避开适当的协议。</p><p><em>路透社</em>发现，一些 SpaceX 工厂的受伤率远高于每 100 名工人 0.8 人受伤或患病的行业平均水平。在德克萨斯州布朗斯维尔工厂，2022 年工伤率为每 100 名工人 4.8 人。在加利福尼亚州霍桑的制造工厂，该数值为 1.8。在该公司进行火箭测试的得克萨斯州麦格雷戈，受伤率为 2.7 人。</p><span id="end-legacy-contents"></span><p>员工们遭受了骨折、割伤、手指压伤、烧伤、电击和严重的头部受伤，其中包括 2021 年布朗斯维尔工人弗洛伦蒂诺·里奥斯 (Florentino Rios) 失明的一次受伤，以及自 2022 年 1 月以来另一次导致员工弗朗西斯科·卡巴达 (Francisco Cabada) 昏迷的情况。在 SpaceX 的麦格雷戈工厂，一名员工2014 年，工人朗尼·勒布朗 (Lonnie LeBlanc) 被风从一辆装载不当的卡车的拖车上吹落而身亡。然而多年来，SpaceX 仅因其安全失误而支付了微薄的罚款。据<em>路透社报道</em>，勒布朗去世后，该公司以 7,000 美元与 OSHA 达成和解。</p><p><em>路透社</em>采访了超过 20 名现任或前任员工，以及其他“了解 SpaceX 安全实践”的人。 SpaceX 的一位前经理告诉<em>路透社</em>，“工人们自己照顾自己的安全”，其他人则表示，员工甚至被告知不要佩戴鲜艳的安全装备，因为马斯克不喜欢它。据<em>路透社报道</em>，SpaceX 在其历史的大部分时间里也多次未能向监管机构提交伤害数据。</p>本文最初发表在 Engadget 上：https://www.engadget.com/spacex-workers-face-above-average-injury-rates-as-musk-prioritizes-mars-over-safety-report-finds-224235095.html ?src=rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/spacex-workers-face-above-average-injury-rates-as-musk-prioritizes-mars-over-safety-report-finds-224235095.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> 76a8e639-cc02-4a03-9657-6e0baf509c03</guid><dc:creator>夏安·麦克唐纳</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>恩杰特</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder>恩杰特</dc:rightsholder><pubDate>Sat, 11 Nov 2023 22:42:35 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1699742571</ingested><modified> 2023-11-11T22:42:53+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Cheyenne MacDonald]]></category><media:content height="3333" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-11/65679c30-80e1-11ee-af76-3436e09345d9" width="5000"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="3333" medium="image" url="https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-11/65679c30-80e1-11ee-af76-3436e09345d9" width="5000"><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[2]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[Veronica Cardenas / reuters]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[SpaceX's Starship rocket prototypes are seen at the SpaceX Starbase in Brownsville, Texas, U.S., August 19, 2023. REUTERS/Veronica G. Cardenas. To match Special Report SPACEX-MUSK/SAFETY]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[SPACEX-MUSK/SAFETY]]></media:title></media:content></item><item><title><![CDATA[Netflix is bringing Hades, Braid and Death's Door to mobile devices]]></title><description type="html"><![CDATA[<p> Netflix 目前拥有<a data-i13n="elm:context_link;elmt:doNotAffiliate;cpos:1;pos:1" class="no-affiliate-link" href="https://www.engadget.com/netflix-plans-to-add-roughly-40-more-titles-to-its-mobile-game-library-this-year-140014333.html" data-original-link="https://www.engadget.com/netflix-plans-to-add-roughly-40-more-titles-to-its-mobile-game-library-this-year-140014333.html">超过 80 款游戏</a>，订阅者可以在 iOS 和 Android（ <a data-i13n="elm:context_link;elmt:doNotAffiliate;cpos:2;pos:1" class="no-affiliate-link" href="https://www.engadget.com/netflix-starts-testing-game-streaming-on-select-devices-smart-tvs-and-desktop-browsers-175241762.html" data-original-link="https://www.engadget.com/netflix-starts-testing-game-streaming-on-select-devices-smart-tvs-and-desktop-browsers-175241762.html">某些情况下</a>还包括电视和台式机）上免费畅玩。作为极客周活动的一部分，该公司透露了更多即将推出该服务的游戏，其中包括一些独立经典游戏。</p><p> <a data-i13n="elm:context_link;elmt:doNotAffiliate;cpos:3;pos:1" class="no-affiliate-link" href="https://www.engadget.com/tag/hades/" data-original-link="https://www.engadget.com/tag/hades/"><em>《Hades》</em></a>是<a data-i13n="elm:context_link;elmt:doNotAffiliate;cpos:4;pos:1" class="no-affiliate-link" href="https://www.engadget.com/best-games-2020-163051873.html" data-original-link="https://www.engadget.com/best-games-2020-163051873.html">2020 年最好的游戏</a>之一，很快将向 iOS 版 Netflix 订阅者推出，但暂时无法在 Android 版上推出。这是一款 Rogue-lite 地下城探索游戏，非常注重可重玩性。</p><span id="end-legacy-contents"></span><p>你将扮演地狱王子萨格勒斯。每当他死时（这可能是经常发生的），他就会回到起点。每次玩的时候都会有所不同，但从一次游戏到下一次游戏，你都会携带知识以及一些武器和能力。 <a data-i13n="elm:context_link;elmt:doNotAffiliate;cpos:5;pos:1" class="no-affiliate-link" href="https://www.engadget.com/hades-wins-2021-hugo-award-173943441.html" data-original-link="https://www.engadget.com/hades-wins-2021-hugo-award-173943441.html">荣获雨果奖的</a>《哈迪斯<em>》</em>也拥有丰富的角色阵容。这是一种真正的享受，你可能会发现自己在其中投入了数百个小时。 </p><div id="e33ae68376a24071b13a56bc7a7f6333"><iframe width="560" height="315" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/iRDeQoad80s" title="YouTube 视频播放器" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen></iframe></div><p>经典时间操控平台游戏<em>《时空幻境》</em>即将登陆 iOS 和 Android 平台，供 Netflix 用户使用。 <a data-i13n="elm:context_link;elmt:doNotAffiliate;cpos:6;pos:1" class="no-affiliate-link" href="https://www.engadget.com/braid-anniversary-edition-early-2021-203037658.html" data-original-link="https://www.engadget.com/braid-anniversary-edition-early-2021-203037658.html">拖延已久的《时空幻境》周年纪念版</a><em>&nbsp;</em>具有升级的音频、手工重新绘制的视觉效果、新鲜的动画“以及一个需要解决的全新谜题世界”。此外，还有超过 15 小时的评论，深入探讨游戏设计、编程和开发的其他方面。 <em>《时空幻境》</em>创作者 Jonathan Blow 透露，新版<em>《时空幻境》</em>将于 4 月 30 日登陆 Netflix 游戏、Windows、PlayStation 和 Xbox </p><div id="e21193e29fdd47dab844c3428d5d0c30"><iframe width="560" height="315" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/LT4xGOC0Bo8?si=BBHhnHFcIK_g1cg0" title="YouTube 视频播放器" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen></iframe></div><p> <a data-i13n="elm:context_link;elmt:doNotAffiliate;cpos:7;pos:1" class="no-affiliate-link" href="https://www.engadget.com/deaths-door-playstation-november-23-213345948.html" data-original-link="https://www.engadget.com/deaths-door-playstation-november-23-213345948.html"><em>《死亡之门》</em></a>是<a data-i13n="elm:context_link;elmt:doNotAffiliate;cpos:8;pos:1" class="no-affiliate-link" href="https://www.engadget.com/engadget-staff-best-favorite-games-2021-150045585.html" data-original-link="https://www.engadget.com/engadget-staff-best-favorite-games-2021-150045585.html">2021 年最出色的独立游戏</a>之一，这款塞尔达传说风格的冒险游戏很快将成为 Netflix 订户的手机独占游戏。你控制一只乌鸦，它的任务是为收割委员会总部收集灵魂，这是一个来世的官僚实体。 </p><div id="c38c03c4d24146eebf517fe9343fc4ed"><iframe width="560" height="315" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/S7vAj-PZfhE" title="YouTube 视频播放器" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen></iframe></div><p>流畅的动作平台游戏<a data-i13n="elm:context_link;elmt:doNotAffiliate;cpos:9;pos:1" class="no-affiliate-link" href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=CaBM1HPD9xI" data-original-link="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=CaBM1HPD9xI"><em>《武士零》</em></a> <em>&nbsp;</em> Netflix Games 以及一系列<a data-i13n="elm:context_link;elmt:doNotAffiliate;cpos:10;pos:1" class="no-affiliate-link" href="https://www.engadget.com/netflix-will-reportedly-turn-more-of-its-hit-shows-into-games-230944708.html" data-original-link="https://www.engadget.com/netflix-will-reportedly-turn-more-of-its-hit-shows-into-games-230944708.html">基于该公司的节目和电影的</a>游戏也即将登陆 Netflix Games。 <em>《Shadow and Bone: Enter the Fold》</em>以该剧前两季为背景， <a data-i13n="elm:context_link;elmt:doNotAffiliate;cpos:11;pos:1" class="no-affiliate-link" href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=6q58KdBX2vE" data-original-link="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=6q58KdBX2vE">现已上线</a>。自上而下的抢劫游戏<a data-i13n="elm:context_link;elmt:doNotAffiliate;cpos:12;pos:1" class="no-affiliate-link" href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=qnDdUVywZMY" data-original-link="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=qnDdUVywZMY"><em>《小鸡快跑：Eggtraction》</em></a> <em>&nbsp;</em>合作动作角色扮演游戏<a data-i13n="elm:context_link;elmt:doNotAffiliate;cpos:13;pos:1" class="no-affiliate-link" href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=gsqi4sPBLwY" data-original-link="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=gsqi4sPBLwY"><em>《龙太子：萨迪亚》</em></a>将于 2024 年推出。</p><p>一款基于 Netflix 热门作品之一的游戏也即将推出。在<em>Money Heist</em>中，您将参与该系列原创系列中的抢劫版本。 Netflix 表示，该游戏将与衍生剧<em>《柏林》</em>一起推出。 </p><div id="48fac2149403414c8e296f48439b9168"><iframe width="560" height="315" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/ONtyhY_DVhE" title="YouTube 视频播放器" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen></iframe></div><p></p>本文最初发表在 Engadget 上：https://www.engadget.com/netflix-is-bringing-hades-braid-and-deaths-door-to-mobile-devices-214008933.html?src=rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/netflix-is-bringing-hades-braid-and-deaths-door-to-mobile-devices-214008933.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> 37a79812-18ea-4d4c-8807-6e633777612c</guid><dc:creator>克里斯·霍尔特</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>恩杰特</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder>恩杰特</dc:rightsholder><pubDate>Sat, 11 Nov 2023 21:40:08 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1699558077</ingested><modified> 2023-11-09T19:28:02+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Consumer Discretionary]]></category><category><![CDATA[Media]]></category><category><![CDATA[Video Games]]></category><category><![CDATA[Arts & Entertainment]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Kris Holt]]></category><media:content height="1079" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2020-09/e2074a30-f906-11ea-af6f-8dfac7947c5a" width="1920"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="1079" medium="image" url="https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2020-09/e2074a30-f906-11ea-af6f-8dfac7947c5a" width="1920"><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[2]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[&#39;Hades&#39; suddenly lands on Nintendo Switch]]></media:title></media:content></item><item><title><![CDATA[SAG-AFTRA deal includes a $40 million streaming bonus and AI protections]]></title><description type="html"><![CDATA[<p>在周二开始的批准投票之前， <a data-i13n="elm:context_link;elmt:doNotAffiliate;cpos:1;pos:1" class="no-affiliate-link" href="https://www.sagaftra.org/sag-aftra-national-board-approves-tentative-agreement-recommends-ratification-2023-tvtheatrical" data-original-link="https://www.sagaftra.org/sag-aftra-national-board-approves-tentative-agreement-recommends-ratification-2023-tvtheatrical"><ins>SAG-AFTRA</ins></a>公布了有关其与好莱坞电影公司高管的临时协议的更多信息。演员工会<a data-i13n="elm:context_link;elmt:doNotAffiliate;cpos:2;pos:1" class="no-affiliate-link" href="https://www.engadget.com/sag-aftra-ends-strike-after-securing-a-deal-that-protects-members-from-the-threat-of-ai-035253314.html" data-original-link="https://www.engadget.com/sag-aftra-ends-strike-after-securing-a-deal-that-protects-members-from-the-threat-of-ai-035253314.html">于11月8日宣布达成协议</a>，结束了长达近四个月的罢工。</p><p>根据协议，从批准之日起至 2025 年 7 月，演员的工资将获得三次加薪：立即加薪 7%，随后在 2024 年 7 月加薪 4%，在 2025 年 7 月加薪 3.5%。对于背景演员，将有截至 11 月 12 日，工资上涨 11%，随后在 2024 年 7 月和 2025 年 7 月分别上涨 4% 和 3.5%。</p><span id="end-legacy-contents"></span><p>它还为一些作品已登陆流媒体平台的成员提供奖金，尽管数额比工会最初要求的要少得多。据<a data-i13n="elm:context_link;elmt:doNotAffiliate;cpos:3;pos:1" class="no-affiliate-link" href="https://variety.com/2023/biz/news/sag-aftra-streaming-bonus-40-million-1235784773/" data-original-link="https://variety.com/2023/biz/news/sag-aftra-streaming-bonus-40-million-1235784773/"><em><ins>Variety</ins></em></a>报道，在该协议的三年期限内，除了正常的流媒体剩余费用之外，还将向演员支付每年 4000 万美元的奖金。但要获得资格，相关节目或电影必须满足某些“成功”标准，这只会成为“这些平台上的微不足道的节目”，SAG-AFTRA 主席<a data-i13n="elm:context_link;elmt:doNotAffiliate;cpos:4;pos:1" class="no-affiliate-link" href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=joEbGiDdDpM" data-original-link="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=joEbGiDdDpM"><ins>Fran Drescher</ins></a>在星期五。</p><p>关于工作室对人工智能的使用，该协议将要求“创建和使用我们在世和已故成员的数字复制品，无论是在片场创建还是获得使用许可，都需要获得知情同意和补偿。”它还为 SAG-AFTRA 工人的健康和退休福利提供了更高的捐款，并旨在结束有色人种演员称之为种族主义的长期发型和化妆做法，例如“不恰当的假发和彩绘”。该协议还要求在性爱场景和涉及裸体的场景中使用亲密协调员，或者如果演员另有要求的话。</p><p> SAG-AFTRA 国家委员会以 86% 的赞成票批准了该协议，现在成员们将有机会参与进来。批准投票期将于 11 月 14 日星期二开始，一直持续到 12 月 5 日。</p>本文最初发表在 Engadget 上：https://www.engadget.com/sag-aftra-deal-includes-a-40-million-streaming-bonus-and-ai-protections-204526458.html?src=rss]] >; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/sag-aftra-deal-includes-a-40-million-streaming-bonus-and-ai-protections-204526458.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> 18f50e22-bfd6-4a08-bd18-b492ef604207</guid><dc:creator>夏安·麦克唐纳</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>恩杰特</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder>恩杰特</dc:rightsholder><pubDate>Sat, 11 Nov 2023 20:45:26 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1699735527</ingested><modified> 2023-11-11T20:45:31+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Cheyenne MacDonald]]></category><media:content height="3603" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-11/e65849d0-80d1-11ee-bbae-6b1df330d4b7" width="5404"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="3603" medium="image" url="https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-11/e65849d0-80d1-11ee-bbae-6b1df330d4b7" width="5404"><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[2]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[Mike Blake / reuters]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[SAG-AFTRA union President Fran Drescher speaks to the media, next to SAG-AFTRA chief negotiator Duncan Crabtree-Ireland, after SAG-AFTRA TV/Theatrical Committee approved a tentative agreement with the Alliance of Motion Picture and Television Producers (AMPTP) to bring an end to the actors strike, in Los Angeles, California, U.S., November 10, 2023. REUTERS/Mike Blake]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[TELEVISION-ACTORS/DEAL]]></media:title></media:content></item><item><title><![CDATA[Dbrand’s artisan keycaps are here to curse you out and stab you]]></title><description type="html"><![CDATA[<p>小工具配件制造商<a data-i13n="elm:context_link;elmt:doNotAffiliate;cpos:1;pos:1" class="no-affiliate-link" href="https://dbrand.com/shop/special-edition/keycaps" data-original-link="https://dbrand.com/shop/special-edition/keycaps">Dbrand</a>发布了一对新颖的机械键盘键帽，它们就像粉丝们想象的那样荒谬。几个月来，该公司一直在宣传其手工键帽，今天恰逢 Dbrand 成立 12 周年纪念日。</p><p>其中一个铝制键帽是 Escape 键的替代品，它是一个金字塔状的设计，当你按下它时，它会刺伤你——因为，根据 Dbrand 半开玩笑的声明，“没有逃脱的余地。”第二个是 Enter 键，并向看到它的人显示一条消息：“F off”。它们都有黑色、银色和彩色新铬色可供选择。 </p><span id="end-legacy-contents"></span><div id="87b39897ee3a4ef3858675ea2e2db43a"><blockquote class="twitter-tweet"><p lang="en" dir="ltr">2011年11月11日，dbrand成立。<br><br> 12 年后，我们正在制造刺痛您的键帽。进步。 <a href="https://t.co/ZHXCJT07Rz">https://t.co/ZHXCJT07Rz</a> <a href="https://t.co/RjhN34sf0L">pic.twitter.com/RjhN34sf0L</a></p> — dbrand (@dbrand) <a href="https://twitter.com/dbrand/status/1723204085623484876?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">2023 年 11 月 11 日</a></blockquote></div><p>Dbrand 通过<a data-i13n="elm:context_link;elmt:doNotAffiliate;cpos:2;pos:1" class="no-affiliate-link" href="https://novelkeys.com/collections/dbrand" data-original-link="https://novelkeys.com/collections/dbrand">NovelKeys</a>出售键帽，售价为 60 美元（Pyramid）——几乎是其 PS5 Darkplates 的价格——以及 40 美元（F*** Off）的有限降价。他们将分两批发货，第一批立即发货，第二批则在 11 月的最后一周发货。</p>本文最初发表在 Engadget 上，网址为 https://www.engadget.com/dbrands-artisan-keycaps-are-here-to-curse-you-out-and-stab-you-170254661.html?src=rss]] >; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/dbrands-artisan-keycaps-are-here-to-curse-you-out-and-stab-you-170254661.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> 94ef7cd7-ebe3-4915-8f10-ee2382fee1a9</guid><dc:creator>夏安·麦克唐纳</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>恩杰特</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder>恩杰特</dc:rightsholder><pubDate>Sat, 11 Nov 2023 17:02:54 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1699723145</ingested><modified> 2023-11-11T17:19:07+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Cheyenne MacDonald]]></category><media:content height="1080" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-11/ecd828e0-80b1-11ee-b79f-664432090da2" width="1920"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="1080" medium="image" url="https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-11/ecd828e0-80b1-11ee-b79f-664432090da2" width="1920"><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[2]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[Dbrand/NovelKeys]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[Dbrand's Pyramid and F*** Off keycaps in silver and neochrome]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[Dbrand keycaps]]></media:title></media:content></item><item><title><![CDATA[Netflix teases the live-action YuYu Hakusho series before it arrives in December]]></title><description type="html"><![CDATA[<p>经典少年漫画和动画<em>《游游白书</em>》的真人改编版将于 12 月 14 日在 Netflix 上播出，该流媒体服务让粉丝们对简短的预告视频有了一些了解。动漫节目的真人改编很受欢迎。其中一些影片，如 Netflix 的<a data-i13n="cpos:1;pos:1" href="https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/death_note_2017"><em>《死亡笔记》</em></a> ，普遍受到批评且反响不佳，而另一些影片，如由佐藤<em>健</em>主演的《浪客剑心》和 Netflix 的<a data-i13n="cpos:2;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/2020-01-29-netflix-one-piece-live-action.html"><em>《海贼王》</em></a>则成功赢得了现有粉丝和新观众的青睐。</p><p>作为富坚义弘的<em>《游游白书》</em>的长期粉丝，我亲眼目睹了其他粉丝在流媒体服务发布该系列的第一张海报后对它的到来感到恐惧。他们说，某些演员选错了，甚至<em>幽游白书的</em>舞台制作中的演员也有更好的服装和造型。然而，预告片实际上看起来相当不错，粉丝们<a data-i13n="cpos:3;pos:1" href="https://www.reddit.com/r/YuYuHakusho/comments/17sexwa/the_teaser_trailer_for_the_liveaction_adaptation/">似乎希望</a>该剧最终能成为更好的动漫改编作品。</p><span id="end-legacy-contents"></span><p>当 Netflix 宣布该剧的播出日期时，它暗示这不会是漫画和动画的精确复制品。 “该系列为故事注入了新的活力，新老粉丝都可以期待以前所未有的方式遇到他们最喜欢的角色，”它说。预告片太短，无法透露节目所做的大部分变化，但眼尖的观众可能会在下面的视频中发现一些变化。 </p><div id="1c9620a034d0448797c23de2ab5eaba5"><iframe src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/GMi-DDJtExs?rel=0" style="top:0;left:0;width:100%;height:100%;position:absolute;border:0;" allowfullscreen="" scrolling="no" data-embed-domain="www.youtube.com"></iframe></div><p></p>本文最初发表在 Engadget 上：https://www.engadget.com/netflix-teases-the-live-action-yuyu-hakusho-series-before-it-arrives-in-december-140055463.html?src=rss ]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/netflix-teases-the-live-action-yuyu-hakusho-series-before-it-arrives-in-december-140055463.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> a1f8cde8-5c6d-4a0d-b366-c892b3ce2c24</guid><dc:creator>玛丽埃拉·穆恩</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>恩杰特</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder>恩杰特</dc:rightsholder><pubDate>Sat, 11 Nov 2023 14:00:55 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1699713202</ingested><modified> 2023-11-11T14:33:25+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Media]]></category><category><![CDATA[Arts & Entertainment]]></category><category><![CDATA[Cartoons & Comics]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Mariella Moon]]></category><media:content height="797" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-11/31e8cd80-809f-11ee-b2ee-bcd6bc820c71" width="1600"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="797" medium="image" url="https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-11/31e8cd80-809f-11ee-b2ee-bcd6bc820c71" width="1600"><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[2]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[Netflix]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[A small man with long hair riding on the shoulder of a larger man wearing sunglasses.]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[YuYu Hakusho]]></media:title></media:content></item><item><title><![CDATA[Netflix's The Witcher: Sirens of the Deep animated film will feature Geralt's original voice actor]]></title><description type="html"><![CDATA[<p> <a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Netflix;elmt:;cpos:1;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=2a170a1e-7e5c-4edd-b5dd-ea6d3bd9416a&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Netflix&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsImxhbmRpbmdVcmwiOiJodHRwczovL3d3dy5uZXRmbGl4LmNvbS90dWR1bS9hcnRpY2xlcy93aXRjaGVyLXNpcmVucy1vZi10aGUtZGVlcC1yZWxlYXNlLWRhdGUtcGhvdG9zIiwiY29udGVudFV1aWQiOiJkNGZmNGQyMy05ZDk2LTQ0YzMtYTJiNy02YmEwMGExMWY4OGQifQ&amp;signature=AQAAAft4wLbTv3j8YgHDHavHymJ36gIZfJpZ_uhg0Z9UyOpo&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.netflix.com%2Ftudum%2Farticles%2Fwitcher-sirens-of-the-deep-release-date-photos" class="rapid-with-clickid" data-original-link="https://www.netflix.com/tudum/articles/witcher-sirens-of-the-deep-release-date-photos">Netflix</a>让《巫师》粉丝们首次观看了一部新动画电影，该电影将于 2024 年底在流媒体服务上上线。 <em>《巫师：深海塞壬》</em>改编自宇宙创造者安杰伊·萨普科夫斯基 (Andrzej Sapkowski) 创作的短篇小说<em>《一点牺牲》</em> 。影片将让利维亚的杰洛特调查一个海滨村庄发生的一系列袭击事件，当时该村庄的人类居民与来自海洋的人鱼之间的冲突不断升级。 Netflix 表示，这部电影的背景设定在真人剧集第一季的第 5 集和第 6 集之间，并且确实表明：电影中的杰洛特比游戏中的杰洛特更像原版《巫师》演员亨利·卡维尔。</p><p>真人版明星安雅·查洛特拉和乔伊·贝蒂也将在动画电影中继续饰演温格堡的叶奈法和贾斯基尔。但杰洛特将由道格·科克尔（Doug Cockle）配音，他因在《巫师》游戏中为白狼配音而闻名。这部电影由康熙哲执导，他曾担任<a data-i13n="cpos:2;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/nightmare-of-the-wolf-trailer-voice-cast-172150913.html"><em>《巫师：狼之噩梦》的</em></a>故事板艺术家，该片讲述了维瑟米尔在成为杰洛特导师之前的故事。它也是由 Studio MIR 制作的，该工作室也是制作<em>《狼的噩梦》的</em>韩国工作室。</p><span id="end-legacy-contents"></span><p>这部电影可能是那些特别喜欢卡维尔扮演杰洛特的人最后一次看到他的<em>版本</em>扮演这个角色。他在真人秀第三季结束后离开了，并由<a data-i13n="cpos:3;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/netflix-renews-the-witcher-season-four-recasts-geralt-of-rivia-201602903.html?_fsig=yugOT_fzX2gV6R2lNvqXJA--%7EA">利亚姆·海姆斯沃斯</a>接替。 </p><div id="79a479a458d44f68b70c64af4cb687b5"><div style="left:0;width:100%;height:0;position:relative;padding-bottom:56.25%;"><iframe src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/Y7ZgJCl62sA?rel=0" style="top:0;left:0;width:100%;height:100%;position:absolute;border:0;" allowfullscreen scrolling="no" data-embed-domain="www.youtube.com"></iframe></div></div><p></p>本文最初发表在 Engadget 上：https://www.engadget.com/netflixs-the-witcher-sirens-of-the-deep-animated-film-will-feature-geralts-original-voice-actor-120020251.html ?src=rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/netflixs-the-witcher-sirens-of-the-deep-animated-film-will-feature-geralts-original-voice-actor-120020251.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> d4ff4d23-9d96-44c3-a2b7-6ba00a11f88d</guid><dc:creator>玛丽埃拉·穆恩</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>恩杰特</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder>恩杰特</dc:rightsholder><pubDate>Sat, 11 Nov 2023 12:00:20 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1699701363</ingested><modified> 2023-11-11T11:16:09+00:00</modified><category><![CDATA[Professional Services]]></category><category><![CDATA[Movie Reviews]]></category><category><![CDATA[Movies]]></category><category><![CDATA[Media]]></category><category><![CDATA[Celebrities]]></category><category><![CDATA[Arts & Entertainment]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Mariella Moon]]></category><media:content height="981" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-11/5d405ab0-807d-11ee-bdff-025c99f20361" width="1600"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="981" medium="image" url="https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-11/5d405ab0-807d-11ee-bdff-025c99f20361" width="1600"><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[2]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[The Witcher: Sirens of the Deep]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[A 2D drawing of a man with long white hair in armor with a sword on his back in the foreground and a woman with red hair in the background.]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[The Witcher: Sirens of the Deep]]></media:title></media:content></item><item><title><![CDATA[NVIDIA may soon announce new AI chips for China to get around US export restrictions]]></title><description type="html"><![CDATA[<p>英伟达真的非常不想失去中国庞大的人工智能芯片市场的机会。据<a data-i13n="elm:context_link;elmt:doNotAffiliate;cpos:1;pos:1" class="no-affiliate-link" href="https://www.wsj.com/tech/nvidia-develops-new-ai-chips-again-to-keep-selling-to-china-d6977a03?st=b9nqhs4y78r65k2&amp;mod=googlenewsfeed" data-original-link="https://www.wsj.com/tech/nvidia-develops-new-ai-chips-again-to-keep-selling-to-china-d6977a03?st=b9nqhs4y78r65k2&amp;mod=googlenewsfeed"><em>《华尔街日报》</em></a>和<a data-i13n="elm:context_link;elmt:doNotAffiliate;cpos:2;pos:1" class="no-affiliate-link" href="https://www.reuters.com/technology/nvidia-plans-release-three-new-chips-china-local-media-2023-11-09/" data-original-link="https://www.reuters.com/technology/nvidia-plans-release-three-new-chips-china-local-media-2023-11-09/"><em>路透社报道</em></a>，该公司正在开发三款专门针对中国的新型人工智能芯片，这些芯片不会违反美国最新的出口限制。去年，美国政府<a data-i13n="cpos:3;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/nvidia-government-rule-restricting-export-ai-chips-china-russia-061846437.html?_fsig=z2L0ZlSgS6oqhw9luRLNZQ--%7EA">通知这家芯片制造商</a>，由于担心这些组件可能用于军事目的，将限制向俄罗斯和中国出口用于超级计算机和人工智能应用的计算机芯片。该规定禁止 NVIDIA 在中国销售某些 A100 和 H100 芯片，因此它专门针对中国市场设计了 A800 和 H800 芯片。</p><p>然而，美国政府最近发布了一套更新的限制，对出口到上述国家的芯片的计算能力进行了限制。根据新规定，A800 和 H800 以及 NVIDIA 的其他产品（ <a data-i13n="cpos:4;pos:1" href="https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-11-09/nvidia-to-release-three-new-ai-chips-for-china-report-says?sref=10lNAhZ9">包括</a>顶级<a data-i13n="cpos:5;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/nvidia-rtx-4090-review-gpu-unholy-amounts-power-130020430.html">RTX 4090</a>消费类 GPU）不再符合出口资格。一些<a data-i13n="cpos:6;pos:1" href="https://fortune.com/2023/11/01/nvidia-shares-fall-report-us-export-rules-cancel-5-billion-advanced-chip-orders-china/">报道甚至暗示</a>该公司最终可能会取消在中国价值超过 50 亿美元的先进芯片订单。</p><span id="end-legacy-contents"></span><p>根据发送给分销商的规格，面向中国市场的新芯片被称为 HGX H20、L20 和 L2。虽然 H20 应该是这三款产品中最强大的型号，但它们都没有超出美国政府新出口规则规定的计算能力阈值。这意味着将它们用于人工智能应用的客户可能需要比使用更高规格模型更多的芯片。</p><p>包括百度、华为、小米和Oppo在内的中国公司已经开始<a data-i13n="cpos:7;pos:1" href="https://www.protocol.com/china/chinese-companies-make-own-semiconductors">设计自己的半导体</a>，为未来可能不再能够从美国和<a data-i13n="cpos:8;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/us-netherlands-and-japan-reportedly-agree-to-limit-chinas-access-to-chipmaking-equipment-174204303.html?_fsig=6vBTho.1YW4we5SVfhB7GQ--%7EA">其他国家</a>进口芯片做准备。然而，由于该公司的声誉和软件，NVIDIA 的老客户可能更喜欢坚持使用该公司的组件， <em>《华尔街日报》</em>称其软件是人工智能开发中最强大的组件之一。据消息人士透露，NVIDIA 最快可能会在 11 月 16 日发布新芯片，并在年底前开始销售。</p>本文最初发表在 Engadget 上：https://www.engadget.com/nvidia-may-soon-announce-new-ai-chips-for-china-to-get-around-us-export-restrictions-100509873.html ?src=rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/nvidia-may-soon-announce-new-ai-chips-for-china-to-get-around-us-export-restrictions-100509873.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> 9b55505b-cfa8-4c00-abc5-882112f37173</guid><dc:creator>玛丽埃拉·穆恩</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>恩杰特</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder>恩杰特</dc:rightsholder><pubDate>Sat, 11 Nov 2023 10:05:09 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1699697072</ingested><modified> 2023-11-11T10:04:37+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Technology & Electronics]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Mariella Moon]]></category><media:content height="2160" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-02/39978970-b388-11ed-bbdf-68ca8f4d4131" width="3240"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="2160" medium="image" url="https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-02/39978970-b388-11ed-bbdf-68ca8f4d4131" width="3240"><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[2]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[Handout . / reuters]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[The logo of NVIDIA as seen at its corporate headquarters in Santa Clara, California, in May of 2022. Courtesy NVIDIA/Handout via REUTERS THIS IMAGE HAS BEEN SUPPLIED BY A THIRD PARTY.  MANDATORY CREDIT]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[NVIDIA-FOXCONN/]]></media:title></media:content></item><item><title><![CDATA[Amazon reportedly blocks 'junk ads' on Apple product pages]]></title><description type="html"><![CDATA[<p>据<a data-i13n="cpos:1;pos:1" href="https://www.businessinsider.com/amazon-gives-apple-special-treatment-while-others-suffer-junk-ads-2023-11"><em>Insider 报道</em></a>，亚马逊对苹果的产品页面给予特殊待遇，并使其相对不含不相关的广告，这标志着两家公司之间的安排。当联邦贸易委员会在 9 月份对这家电子商务零售商<a data-i13n="cpos:2;pos:1" href="https://www.ftc.gov/news-events/news/press-releases/2023/09/ftc-sues-amazon-illegally-maintaining-monopoly-power">提起反垄断诉讼</a>时，指控亚马逊“故意增加垃圾广告，从而降低搜索质量”。然而， <em>Insider</em>发现，“iPhone”和“iPad”等苹果产品的页面显示干净的页面布局，没有广告或推荐。与此同时，三星 Galaxy 和 Microsoft Surface 等竞争对手品牌的产品会显示多个横幅广告和其他品牌的一些赞助推荐。</p><p>我们自己尝试了一下，确实发现苹果的产品页面看起来确实更干净。然而，微软 Surface Pro 展示了“4 星及以上”的赞助列表轮播，以及与特定商品相关的产品和多个横幅广告。 <em>Insider</em>称，根据众议院司法委员会分享的一封电子邮件，苹果早在 2018 年就要求亚马逊保持其产品页面上没有杂乱的广告。据报道，时任亚马逊零售首席执行官的杰夫·威尔克（Jeff Wilke）写道：“我们知道，苹果不想在搜索或详情页面上推动竞争品牌的销售。”</p><span id="end-legacy-contents"></span><p>苹果公司向该出版物承认，它与亚马逊达成了某种协议，禁止其他公司在后者的市场上购买“与苹果相关的特定品牌查询”的广告。他们仍然可以购买带有 Apple 名称的关键短语的广告，例如“iPad 键盘壳”，但不能购买“iPad”本身的广告。苹果代表在一份声明中表示：“苹果签署这些协议的目标是创造尽可能最佳的客户体验，其他公司也可以这样做。”他们补充说，这笔交易还旨在解决该公司在平台上的假冒产品问题，因为在此之前，该公司曾向亚马逊发送“数十万份下架通知”。</p><p>虽然尚不清楚两家公司之间是否进行了资金交换，但众议院分享的电子邮件谈到了潜在的财务交易。据报道，亚马逊一开始拒绝了苹果的请求，但威尔克在电子邮件中写道：“当搜索苹果团队时，我们无法改变我们的自然搜索算法，在搜索结果中只返回苹果产品……苹果需要购买这些展示位置，或者赔偿亚马逊损失的广告收入。”</p>本文最初发表在 Engadget 上：https://www.engadget.com/amazon-reportedly-blocks-junk-ads-on-apple-product-pages-045018125.html?src=rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/amazon-reportedly-blocks-junk-ads-on-apple-product-pages-045018125.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> 928946bc-198a-4ebb-8076-34ef1bb42e37</guid><dc:creator>玛丽埃拉·穆恩</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>恩杰特</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder>恩杰特</dc:rightsholder><pubDate>Sat, 11 Nov 2023 04:50:18 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1699678182</ingested><modified> 2023-11-11T04:49:56+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Information Technology]]></category><category><![CDATA[Technology & Electronics]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Mariella Moon]]></category><media:content height="2334" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-10/8581f400-647d-11ee-bffa-f88443a2d87f" width="3500"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="2334" medium="image" url="https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-10/8581f400-647d-11ee-bffa-f88443a2d87f" width="3500"><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[2]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[VIEW press via Getty Images]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[NEW YORK, NEW YORK - JULY 21: Amazon workers unloading boxes from a truck in Manhattan on July 21, 2023 in New York City. The company will find recyclable alternatives to reemplazed the use of plastic padded bags for parcel shipments in order to impact on the environment, particularly the oceans. (Photo by Kena Betancur/VIEWpress)]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[Amazon Plans To Cut 11.6% Less Plastic Padded Mailers]]></media:title></media:content></item><item><title><![CDATA[Netflix's new 3 Body Problem trailer reveals a delay to March 2024]]></title><description type="html"><![CDATA[<p> Netflix 的新科幻剧推迟到 2024 年 3 月 22 日上映<em>。《3 Body Problem》</em>原定于 2023 年首播，后来推迟到 2024 年 1 月，现在推迟到 3 月。正如最初的延迟伴随着<a data-i13n="cpos:1;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/netflixs-3-body-problem-first-look-confirms-january-2024-premiere-213927002.html">预告片</a>一样，这个也是如此： </p><div id="b765e8323b5b40fb9204c366f45ee87c"><iframe src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/fje8el375T0?rel=0" style="top:0;left:0;width:100%;height:100%;position:absolute;border:0;" allowfullscreen="" scrolling="no" data-embed-domain="www.youtube.com"></iframe></div><p> <em>《3 Body Problem》</em>由大卫·贝尼奥夫 (David Benioff) 和 DB Weiss（HBO<em>电视剧《权力的游戏》的</em>创作者）与编剧亚历山大·吴 (Alexander Woo) 共同改编。新的预告片让我们第一次看到了该系列的关键“视频游戏”《<em>三体》</em> ，其中涉及一个模糊且极其闪亮的 VR 耳机。根据约翰·布拉德利饰演的角色杰克·鲁尼的说法，这款耳机“没有屏幕……没有耳机插孔……甚至没有充电端口”。戴上耳机后，鲁尼进入了一个超现实的世界，然后他被迅速弹出，预告片结束。</p><span id="end-legacy-contents"></span><p>该剧的素材是刘慈欣《追忆地球往事》系列的第一部小说<em>《三体》</em> 。该书最初于 00 年代中期在中国发行，2014 年 Tor Books 出版了英文译本，获得了国际认可并获得了雨果奖。Netflix 于 2020 年宣布对该书语法错误的改编，主演包括本尼迪克特·王 (Benedict Wong)、艾莎·冈萨雷斯 (Eiza González)以及<em>《权力的游戏》的</em>几位演员，包括乔纳森·普赖斯和前面提到的布拉德利。</p>本文最初发表在 Engadget 上：https://www.engadget.com/netflixs-new-3-body-problem-trailer-reveals-a-delay-to-march-2024-004430208.html?src=rss]] >; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/netflixs-new-3-body-problem-trailer-reveals-a-delay-to-march-2024-004430208.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> 3694b4b3-1b47-4908-98a5-0bc14e9b3825</guid><dc:creator>亚伦·索普里斯</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>恩杰特</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder>恩杰特</dc:rightsholder><pubDate>Sat, 11 Nov 2023 00:44:30 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1699713470</ingested><modified> 2023-11-11T14:37:53+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Consumer Discretionary]]></category><category><![CDATA[Books & Publishing]]></category><category><![CDATA[Arts & Entertainment]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Aaron Souppouris]]></category><media:content height="1464" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-11/c6f403e0-809f-11ee-83fd-8df707637486" width="2756"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="1464" medium="image" url="https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-11/c6f403e0-809f-11ee-83fd-8df707637486" width="2756"><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[2]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[Netflix]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[A man and woman sit on a living room couch and both look at a shiny object that the man is holding.]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[3 Body Problem]]></media:title></media:content></item><item><title><![CDATA[Qualcomm's satellite texting plan is dead because phone makers aren't interested]]></title><description type="html"><![CDATA[<p>早在一月份，高通就宣布了<a data-i13n="cpos:1;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/qualcomm-snapdragon-satellite-messaging-android-211037007.html"><ins>Snapdragon Satellite</ins></a>项目，旨在让 Android 用户在没有手机服务时通过卫星发送短信。这将是该公司对苹果<a data-i13n="cpos:2;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/iphone-14-emergency-sos-satellite-connection-183230405.html"><ins>在 iPhone 14 系列中首次推出的</ins></a>紧急求救功能的回应。然而，这一举措并没有像高通所希望的那样取得成果。</p><p>高通公司将终止与卫星电话制造商 Iridium 的 Snapdragon 卫星合作伙伴关系。铱星公司<a data-i13n="cpos:3;pos:1" href="https://investor.iridium.com/2023-11-09-Iridium-Announces-New-D2D-Direction"><ins>在一份声明中表示</ins></a>，尽管两家公司“成功开发并展示了该技术”，但智能手机制造商“尚未将该技术纳入其设备中”。</p><span id="end-legacy-contents"></span><p>高通公司向<a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:CNBC;elmt:;cpos:4;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=34e37b9c-8975-48da-aa39-df8bcd5badc3&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=CNBC&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsImxhbmRpbmdVcmwiOiJodHRwczovL3d3dy5jbmJjLmNvbS8yMDIzLzExLzA5L2lyaWRpdW0tYW5ub3VuY2VzLWVuZC1vZi1xdWFsY29tbS1zYXRlbGxpdGUtdG8tcGhvbmUtcGFydG5lcnNoaXAuaHRtbCIsImNvbnRlbnRVdWlkIjoiZmEyNDk5YjMtY2RjYi00MWViLWExMGMtNmE2N2E0N2UwYzcyIn0&amp;signature=AQAAAUI20565SQSm2LFwxxgax39P0PrfHTD0dROb0MzKNMOd&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbc.com%2F2023%2F11%2F09%2Firidium-announces-end-of-qualcomm-satellite-to-phone-partnership.html" class="rapid-with-clickid" data-original-link="https://www.cnbc.com/2023/11/09/iridium-announces-end-of-qualcomm-satellite-to-phone-partnership.html"><em><ins>CNBC</ins></em></a>表示，智能手机制造商已“表示倾向于采用基于标准的卫星连接解决方​​案”。换句话说，他们正在寻找一种更开放的方法，但不一定将高通定位为中间人。作为<a data-i13n="cpos:5;pos:1" href="https://www.theverge.com/2023/11/10/23955416/qualcomm-snapdragon-satellite-shut-down-emergency-sos-iridium"><em><ins>边缘</ins></em></a><em>&nbsp;</em>指出，卫星短信的成本可能也让一些制造商望而却步。苹果暂时承担紧急求救费用。</p><p>现在，铱星与高通的协议即将结束，它将能够直接与智能手机制造商、移动操作系统开发商和其他芯片制造商合作。与此同时，苹果通过<a data-i13n="cpos:6;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/apple-iphone-15-review-the-most-substantial-update-to-the-regular-iphone-in-years-173204712.html"><ins>在 iPhone 15 中</ins></a>添加碰撞检测集成来扩展其紧急 SOS 功能。</p><p>在其他地方，星链<a data-i13n="cpos:7;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/starlinks-satellite-cell-service-is-set-to-launch-in-2024-but-only-for-sms-215036124.html"><ins>计划于明年推出卫星短信服务</ins></a>。它计划最终直接向手机提供卫星供电的语音和数据功能，这意味着用户不一定需要在附近拥有星链终端。</p>本文最初发表在 Engadget 上：https://www.engadget.com/qualcomms-satellite-texting-plan-is-dead-because-phone-makers-arent-interested-204331091.html?src=rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/qualcomms-satellite-texting-plan-is-dead-because-phone-makers-arent-interested-204331091.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> fa2499b3-cdcb-41eb-a10c-6a67a47e0c72</guid><dc:creator>克里斯·霍尔特</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>恩杰特</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder>恩杰特</dc:rightsholder><pubDate>Fri, 10 Nov 2023 20:43:31 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1699649012</ingested><modified> 2023-11-10T20:43:38+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Information Technology]]></category><category><![CDATA[Commodity Markets]]></category><category><![CDATA[Telecommunication]]></category><category><![CDATA[Technology & Electronics]]></category><category><![CDATA[Handheld & Connected Devices]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Kris Holt]]></category><media:content height="1280" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-01/af272f70-8c95-11ed-bd2f-ace7de5e3924" width="1920"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="1280" medium="image" url="https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-01/af272f70-8c95-11ed-bd2f-ace7de5e3924" width="1920"><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[2]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[Karissa Bell / Engadget]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[A demo version of Qualcomm's satellite messaging tech.]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[Snapdragon Satellite]]></media:title></media:content></item><item><title><![CDATA[The Super Mario Bros. Movie is coming to Netflix on December 3]]></title><description type="html"><![CDATA[<p>你<a data-i13n="cpos:2;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/netflix-jacks-price-of-its-premium-plan-up-to-23-a-month-201116571.html">突然每个月要多付几美元的</a><a data-i13n="cpos:1;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/tag/netflix/">Netflix</a>订阅服务很快就会给你带来更多的物有所值。 <em>《超级马里奥兄弟大电影》</em>是今年迄今为止票房第二高的电影，仅次于<em>《芭比娃娃</em>》，将于 12 月 3 日<a data-i13n="elm:context_link;elmt:doNotAffiliate;cpos:3;pos:1" class="no-affiliate-link" href="https://kotaku.com/the-super-mario-bros-movie-is-on-netflix-where-to-watch-1851012045" data-original-link="https://kotaku.com/the-super-mario-bros-movie-is-on-netflix-where-to-watch-1851012045">在 Netflix 上映</a>。</p><p> <a data-i13n="cpos:4;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/the-super-mario-bros-movie-is-coming-to-peacock-on-august-3rd-184942554.html">自八月初以来，</a>它一直是 Peacock 流媒体独家节目。 Peacock 拥有 2800 万付费订阅者，而 Netflix 在美国拥有<a data-i13n="cpos:5;pos:1" href="https://s22.q4cdn.com/959853165/files/doc_financials/2023/q3/FINAL-Q3-23-Shareholder-Letter.pdf">约</a>7400 万付费会员，因此更多的人将能够在家合法观看这部电影，而无需租用或购买。 </p><span id="end-legacy-contents"></span><div id="b0694f14ce1245f08d443e812d68e7d2"><blockquote class="twitter-tweet"><p lang="en" dir="ltr">对于那些在假期里沉迷于《马里奥赛车》的家庭来说，《超级马里奥兄弟电影》将在 Netflix 上播出，以帮助他们康复。 12月3日！ <a href="https://t.co/5nhvrcJWME">pic.twitter.com/5nhvrcJWME</a></p> — Netflix (@netflix) <a href="https://twitter.com/netflix/status/1722671648640286829?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">2023 年 11 月 9 日</a></blockquote></div><p><em>《超级马里奥兄弟大电影》</em>是<a data-i13n="cpos:6;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/super-mario-bros-movie-review-fun-safe-romp-135146207.html">一次有趣但不出所料的安全蘑菇王国之旅</a>，杰克·布莱克饰演的库巴令人难忘。对于第一次在 Netflix 上观看这部电影的人来说，有一句警告：祝你好运，很快就能把那首《桃子》这首歌从你的脑海中抹掉。哦，克里斯·帕拉特<a data-i13n="cpos:7;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/chris-pratt-and-charlie-day-headline-the-mario-bros-movie-in-2022-230924814.html">饰演马里奥完全没问题</a>！</p><p>尽管《马里奥》电影是有史以来<a data-i13n="cpos:8;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/the-super-mario-bros-movie-is-already-the-biggest-game-adaptation-of-all-time-173946909.html">票房最高的视频游戏系列改编电影</a>，但任天堂及其合作伙伴（环球影业和照明娱乐）尚未宣布不可避免的续集。然而， <a data-i13n="cpos:9;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/nintendo-is-making-a-live-action-legend-of-zelda-movie-221618064.html">本周有消息称</a>，任天堂正在与索尼影业合作拍摄真人版《塞尔达传说》，这似乎是一个风险更大的赌注。</p>本文最初发表在 Engadget 上：https://www.engadget.com/the-super-mario-bros-movie-is-coming-to-netflix-on-december-3-194407138.html?src=rss]] >; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/the-super-mario-bros-movie-is-coming-to-netflix-on-december-3-194407138.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> 6cabbfb2-5f82-4ead-accf-ad53ac53c633</guid><dc:creator>克里斯·霍尔特</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>恩杰特</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder>恩杰特</dc:rightsholder><pubDate>Fri, 10 Nov 2023 19:44:22 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1699645462</ingested><modified> 2023-11-10T19:44:25+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Movie Reviews]]></category><category><![CDATA[Movies]]></category><category><![CDATA[Media]]></category><category><![CDATA[Arts & Entertainment]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Kris Holt]]></category><media:content height="549" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-04/a4bb8ab0-daea-11ed-94f9-5c4f39a1e573" width="976"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="549" medium="image" url="https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-04/a4bb8ab0-daea-11ed-94f9-5c4f39a1e573" width="976"><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[2]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[Universal Pictures/Illumination/Nintendo]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[Mario Mario and Luigi Mario in the The Super Mario Bros. Movie,]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[The Super Mario Bros. Movie]]></media:title></media:content></item></channel></rss>